# AAE4011 Assignment 1 – ROS-Based Vehicle Detection from Rosbag

This repository implements a real-time vehicle detection pipeline for Unmanned Aerial Systems (UAS) using ROS and YOLOv8. The system processes image streams from a provided `.bag` file, detects vehicles (cars, buses, etc.), and visualizes bounding boxes with confidence scores.

